songs.title: Darkshines
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Passing by, you light up my darkest skies
You'll take only seconds to draw me in
So be mine and your innocence
I will consume

[Hook]
Dark shines
Bringing me down
Making my heart feel sore
Cause it's good

[Verse 2]
Hold your hands up to your eyes again
Hide from the scary scenes, suppress your fears
So be mine and your innocence
I will consume

[Hook]
Dark shines
Bringing me down
Making my heart feel sore
Cause it's good
Your dark shines
Bringing me down
Making my heart feel sore
Cause it's good

[Hook]
Dark shines
Bringing me down
Making my heart feel sore
Cause it's good
It's good
